config DISP_EXT_SUB
	bool "To enable the sub display"
	default y
	---help---
	  Say Y here if you want to enable the sub display.
config DISP_EXT_I2C
	bool "To enable the i2c"
	default y
	---help---
	  Say Y here if you want to enable the i2c.
config DISP_EXT_SUB_ALWAYS_ON
	bool "To enable the always_on"
	default n
	---help---
	  Say Y here if you want to enable the always_on.
config DISP_EXT_SUB_CONTRAST
	bool "To enable the contrast"
	default n
	---help---
	  Say Y here if you want to enable the contrast.
config DISP_EXT_SUB_USER_CONTRAST
	bool "To enable the contrast"
	default n
	---help---
	  Say Y here if you want to enable the contrast.
config DISP_EXT_SPI
	bool "To enable the spi"
	default y
	---help---
	The MDSS debugging provides support to enable display debugging
	features to: Dump MDSS registers during driver errors, panic
	driver during fatal errors and enable some display-driver logging
	into an internal buffer (this avoids logging overhead).
